Veeam Test Task - Jan BÃ­l

Operating system: Linux

usage: synch.py [-h] -s SOURCE_FOLDER -r REPLICA_FOLDER [-i INTERVAL] [-l LOG_FILE]

Synchronizes 2 files periodicaly and logs changes

options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -s SOURCE_FOLDER, --source_folder SOURCE_FOLDER
                        Path of the source folder
  -r REPLICA_FOLDER, --replica_folder REPLICA_FOLDER
                        Path of the replica folder
  -i INTERVAL, --interval INTERVAL
                        Time interval between synchronizations in seconds, default = 10
  -l LOG_FILE, --log_file LOG_FILE
                        Path to a log file, default is log_file.txt